T11TD4247E:200a-1: a'i shva ra b'am ga k'a ri k'a /
T11TD4247E:200a-3: dbang phyug 'jig pa'i tshig le'ur byas pa //
T11TD4247E:200a-4: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T11TD4247E:200a-5: gang gis yang dag mkhyen gyur cing //
T11TD4247E:200a-6: sems can rnams la ston byed pa //
T11TD4247E:200a-8: yang dag gtan la dbab par bya //
T11TD4247E:200a-9: las dang nyon mongs las skyes shing //
T11TD4247E:200a-10: skad cig ma dang de bdag med //
T11TD4247E:200a-11: thams cad mkhyen dang 'dod chags bral //
T11TD4247E:200a-12: bsdus te 'dir ni brjod par bya //
T11TD4247E:200a-13: glen blo gang zhig 'di dag kun //
T11TD4247E:200a-14: dbang phyug gis ni byas so zhes //
T11TD4247E:200a-15: smra ba de yang mi shes pa //
T11TD4247E:200a-16: gzhom phyir 'khor du gsal bar brjod //
T11TD4247E:200a-17: lus dang dbang po sa la sogs //
T11TD4247E:200a-18: thams cad dbang phyug gis ma byas //
T11TD4247E:200a-19: lus 'bras rtogs pa tha dad phyir// dper na rgyu las skyes mthong bzhin //
T11TD4247E:200a-20: de yang dbang phyug bskyed bya na /
T11TD4247E:200a-21: blo ldan skye las grub 'gyur te //
T11TD4247E:200a-22: ji ltar bum pa de bzhin du //
T11TD4247E:200a-23: gzhan zhes gtam du brjod mi bya //
T11TD4247E:200a-24: byed pa la sogs rtag pa yi //
T11TD4247E:200a-25: rgyu las skyes pa ma yin te //
T11TD4247E:200a-26: rim 'jug phyir na dper blo bzhin //
T11TD4247E:200a-27: bdag dang dbang phyug sel bar blta //
T11TD4247E:200a-28: gal te de yang dbang phyug las //
T11TD4247E:200a-29: log pa'i shes pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
T11TD4247E:200a-30: bstan bcos rtsom pa don med de'i //
T11TD4247E:200a-31: rgyu yod pa las skye phyir ro //
T11TD4247E:200a-32: dngos po dbyangs dang ldan pa rnams //
T11TD4247E:200a-33: blo dang ldan pas byas 'grub pa //
T11TD4247E:200a-34: de yang chos kyi khya par las //
T11TD4247E:200a-35: phyin ci log tu sgrub pa yin //
T11TD4247E:200a-36: lus sogs dbyibs dang ldan pa'i phyir //
T11TD4247E:200a-37: mi rtog du mas bskyed bya bar //
T11TD4247E:200a-38: gzung ste dper na khyim sogs la //
T11TD4247E:200a-39: de bzhin du ni mthong phyir ro //
T11TD4247E:200b-0: @200b blo dang ldan pa'i rgyu can du //
T11TD4247E:200b-1: 'on te spyir ni sgrub byed na //
T11TD4247E:200b-2: sgrub pa sgrub ste gang gi phyir //
T11TD4247E:200b-3: thams cad las las skyes par 'dod //
T11TD4247E:200b-4: dngos rnams brgyan pa nyid do zhes //
T11TD4247E:200b-5: gtan tshigs yongs su bsgrags pa gang //
T11TD4247E:200b-6: de yang ma grub dngos po kun //
T11TD4247E:200b-7: de yi ngo bor 'byung phyir ro //
T11TD4247E:200b-8: gang phyir tha dad grub dngos rnams //
T11TD4247E:200b-9: bkod pa brgyan pa zhes bya na //
T11TD4247E:200b-10: de yang mig la sogs rnams la //
T11TD4247E:200b-11: khyim la sogs bzhin mi snang ngo //
T11TD4247E:200b-12: dbang phyug 'dod pa'i dngos po de //
T11TD4247E:200b-13: dbang sogs yon tan mi ldan te //
T11TD4247E:200b-14: mi skye ba dang mi 'jig bzhin //
T11TD4247E:200b-15: khyab phyir nam mkha'i bdag nyid bzhin //
T11TD4247E:200b-16: rgyu ldan phyir na gzhan gyis bskyed //
T11TD4247E:200b-17: dper na bum pa la sogs bzhin //
T11TD4247E:200b-18: ri bong rva ni ma skyes la //
T11TD4247E:200b-19: rgyu nyid yod pa ma yin no //
T11TD4247E:200b-20: dgos pa med par byed pa ni //
T11TD4247E:200b-21: smyon pa rnams dang mtshungs par 'gyur //
T11TD4247E:200b-24: de la dbang phyug yod mi 'gyur //
T11TD4247E:200b-25: gal te dbang phyug gzhan dag dang //
T11TD4247E:200b-26: las la ltos pa yin na ni //
T11TD4247E:200b-27: de la ltos na de la ni //
T11TD4247E:200b-28: dad pa kho nas dmigs par zad //
T11TD4247E:200b-29: gal te lus sogs gzugs yin na //
T11TD4247E:200b-30: thams cad byed pa ma yin te //
T11TD4247E:200b-31: lus ldan dbang po ldan pa'i phyir //
T11TD4247E:200b-32: byed phyir de las gzhan pa bzhin //
T11TD4247E:200b-33: ji skad bshad pa'i gtan tshigs las //
T11TD4247E:200b-34: dbang phyug skye dang ldan pa dang //
T11TD4247E:200b-35: 'jig dang khyab pa nyid du ni //
T11TD4247E:200b-36: rnam pa kun du thal bar 'gyur //
T11TD4247E:200b-37: dbang phyug 'dod pas byed po na //
T11TD4247E:200b-38: la lar kun du ci phyir min //
T11TD4247E:200b-39: yon tan skyon dag rnam dpyad nas //
T11TD4247E:200b-41: yon tan skyon skye gang yin pa //
T11TD4247E:200b-42: dbang phyug sngon du 'gro yin na //
T11TD4247E:200b-43: des na de dag thams cad du //
T11TD4247E:200b-44: skye ba nyid du thal bar 'gyur //
T11TD4247E:200b-45: de tsam las ni skye ba'i phyir //
T11TD4247E:200b-47: sngar skyes ma yin gang yin te //
T11TD4247E:200b-48: phyis ni ji ltar skye bar 'gyur //
T11TD4247E:200b-49: 'on te shes pa'i ngo bo na //
T11TD4247E:200b-50: dbang po med par ga la zhig / ma sprul pa yi sngon rol du //
T11TD4247E:200b-51: shes bya med par ji ltar shes //
T11TD4247E:200b-52: 'on te mi gsal rang bzhin na //
T11TD4247E:200b-53: rang dbang can du ji ltar sngon //
T11TD4247E:200b-54: 'dod pa skye ba'i rgyu tsam ste //
T11TD4247E:200b-55: dper na chu la sogs bzhin na //
T11TD4247E:200b-56: rgyu yin na yang rtag pa dang //
T11TD4247E:200b-57: ngo bo gcig tu rnam gnas phyir //
T11TD4247E:201a-1: po rnams ni thams cad du //
T11TD4247E:201a-2: rtag tu skye ba nyid du 'gyur //
T11TD4247E:201a-3: rigs pa'i lam gyi rjes 'brangs pa'i //
T11TD4247E:201a-4: mkhas pa'i tshul ni 'di nyid kyis //
T11TD4247E:201a-5: khyab 'jug tshangs pa la sogs pa'ang //
T11TD4247E:201a-6: gsal bar khong du chud par bya //
T11TD4247E:201a-7: dbang phyug 'jig pa'i tshig le'ur byas pa//
T11TD4247E:201a-8: slob dpon dge srungs kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
